{"tid":1701160,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"由養寵物聯想到香港局勢","createTime":"2019-11-09T01:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T01:51:21.000Z","uid":238013,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"63c97241c05aaf3ba3c9ccc5b5d85dae6fbf23dc","tid":1701160,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n本人領養咗兩隻貓，前後隔咗一年先後嚟到我屋企<br />\n先嚟個隻比較熱情，好乖好癡人，所以一年後萌生養多隻陪佢嘅意欲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當二仔嚟到之後，一仔就變咗大佬，雖然二仔年紀大過佢<br />\n一仔想食嘅嘢，二仔唔敢食<br />\n一仔瞓個位，二仔唔敢坐<br />\n一仔打二仔，如果唔係無路可退二仔都唔會還手<br />\n<br />\n二仔地位，到而家都係一仔之下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連動物都明白，先來到的就係主人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">純過綿羊的香港人到今日仲話要包容大陸人</span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人建立的社會，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">住屋比支那人搶晒</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人建立的社會，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">學位比支那人搶晒</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人建立的社會，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">生活空間比支那人污染晒</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人建立的社會，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連法律治安都比支那人支配<br />\n</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人話支持運動，但係自己<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">能力有限上唔到前線，問可以點做咩幫手.</span>..<br />\n<br />\n我話你知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<ins>將杯葛/驅逐入侵者態度變成習慣</ins></span><br />\n- 社會地位/資源吋步不讓，即使平日上車落車、搭lift 食飯都唔會禮讓 （接觸過都知支那人係唔會讓人，你讓佢反而佢覺得自己地位比你高）<br />\n- 有得揀必定揀本土嘢先，四川麻辣/雲南米線個啲食店就咪再幫襯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>戒除貪平貪小便宜習慣</ins><br />\n</span><br />\n- 唔好再貪便宜買咁多垃圾不良品，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">淘寶戒咗佢</span><br />\n- 唔想比人監控就唔好再用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大陸電話</span><br />\n- 唔想比人監控就放棄幾蚊幾毫優惠用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支付寶</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係個個都敢以武制暴，不過對付入侵者你都包容，你一係就學阿叻咁無下一代累人累物，一係就學定做新彊人嘞。<br />\n<br />\n期望支那人會釋出善意包容番你？我隻貓比人剝削都會毫不退讓啦，繼續企文明高地就等死啦。等死呢樣必定成功，必定等到。<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多，<br />\n<ins>香港人再讓步、唔團結就死梗，路係自己行，唔好等人救</ins>"},{"pid":"31e664d474b3fe458f253940d2bbf5f57d6c0a50","tid":1701160,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"早晨 <br />\n記得出門前 上 twitter retweet<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<br />\n（最新!!）Senator Rubio講議員被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=cb330994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846%3Fs%3D19&h=370276c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846?s=19</a><br />\nSenator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=f7bf5ec4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（最新）Senator Scott 都出聲講議員被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=97e1db52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&h=01c0cece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}